右侧的列表中显示了2006年用来给北大西洋热带气旋命名的名称。这份名单与1996年大西洋飓风季基本相同，只有“柯克”（{{lang|en|Kirk}}）例外，用来取代[[飓风基斯|基斯]]（{{lang|en|Keith}}）<ref name="names">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | title = Worldwide Tropical Cyclone Names | year = 2008 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2014-04-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140208064603/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutnames.shtml | archivedate = 2014-02-08 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutnames.shtml }}</ref>。本季没有任何一个名称退役，所以都将在[[2012年大西洋飓风季|2012年大西洋飓风季]]再度使用，这也是继1997年以来第一个没有名称退役的大西洋飓风季<ref>{{cite report | author = Gary Padgett, Jack Beven, James Lewis Free, Sandy Delgado | date = 2012-05-23 | title = Subject: B3) What storm names have been retired? | publisher = Hurricane Research Division | accessdate = 2014-08-22 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/B3.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131111163143/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/B3.html | archivedate = 2013-11-11 }}</ref>。列表中没有命名的名称将以{{tcname unused}}显示。
{{clear}}

== 季节影响 ==

ACE的計算公式：<math>\sum_{}^{} \frac{{v_\mathrm{max}}^2}{10^4},</math>，單位為<math>10^4 kt^2</math>。<ref>本ACE計算資料由NRL提供，採1分鐘平均風速</ref>

